description:
It’s Bobby’s 40th Birthday! He celebrates by helping out a listener going through a rough time. Bobby and his girlfriend review “Ford vs. Ferrari”. Plus, Eddie gets heat for feeding his foster baby “Flaming Hot Cheetos”!
